<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>DeepPulse — Sleep Experience</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;1,300;1,400&family=Spectral:ital,wght@0,200;0,300;1,200&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  :root {
    --ink: #0a0b10;
    --deep: #060810;
    --paper: #f0ede8;
    --mist: #a8b4c4;
    --glow: #7b9ec0;
    --gold: #c8a96e;
    --dim: rgba(168,180,196,0.15);
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--deep);
    color: var(--paper);
    font-family: 'Spectral', Georgia, serif;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    cursor: none;
  }

  /* Custom cursor */
  .cursor {
    position: fixed;
    width: 6px; height: 6px;
    background: var(--glow);
    border-radius: 50%;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9999;
    transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
    transition: transform 0.1s, opacity 0.3s;
    mix-blend-mode: screen;
  }
  .cursor-ring {
    position: fixed;
    width: 32px; height: 32px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(123,158,192,0.4);
    border-radius: 50%;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9998;
    transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
    transition: transform 0.25s ease, width 0.3s, height 0.3s, opacity 0.3s;
  }

  /* Stars background */
  .stars {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .star {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: white;
    animation: twinkle var(--d, 4s) var(--delay, 0s) ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }
  @keyframes twinkle {
    from { opacity: var(--min-op, 0.05); transform: scale(1); }
    to   { opacity: var(--max-op, 0.4);  transform: scale(1.3); }
  }

  /* Slow aurora background */
  .aurora {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 20% 80%, rgba(30,50,90,0.5) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 80% 20%, rgba(20,40,80,0.4) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 100% 60% at 50% 100%, rgba(10,20,50,0.6) 0%, transparent 50%);
    animation: aurora-drift 20s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }
  @keyframes aurora-drift {
    0%   { opacity: 0.6; transform: scale(1) rotate(0deg); }
    100% { opacity: 1;   transform: scale(1.05) rotate(1deg); }
  }

  /* Noise grain overlay */
  body::after {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1000;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='1'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    opacity: 0.025;
  }

  /* Layout */
  section { position: relative; z-index: 10; }

  /* ─── HERO ─────────────────────────────────── */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Spectral', serif;
    font-weight: 200;
    font-size: clamp(0.65rem, 1.5vw, 0.8rem);
    letter-spacing: 0.35em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--glow);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 1.4s 0.3s ease forwards;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 12vw, 9rem);
    line-height: 0.92;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 1.6s 0.5s ease forwards;
    margin-bottom: 0.3em;
  }
  .hero-title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--mist);
    display: block;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-family: 'Spectral', serif;
    font-weight: 200;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 2.5vw, 1.2rem);
    color: var(--mist);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 1.6s 0.8s ease forwards;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    max-width: 36ch;
  }

  /* Breathing orb */
  .orb-wrap {
    position: relative;
    width: 200px; height: 200px;
    margin: 2rem auto 3.5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 1.6s 1s ease forwards;
  }
  .orb {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 40% 35%,
      rgba(123,158,192,0.25) 0%,
      rgba(30,60,120,0.15) 40%,
      transparent 70%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(123,158,192,0.2);
    animation: breathe 8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .orb-inner {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 25%;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 40% 35%,
      rgba(200,169,110,0.18) 0%,
      rgba(123,158,192,0.1) 50%,
      transparent 70%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.15);
    animation: breathe 8s ease-in-out 1s infinite;
  }
  .orb-pulse {
    position: absolute;
    inset: -20%;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(123,158,192,0.08);
    animation: pulse-out 8s ease-out infinite;
  }
  .orb-pulse:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 2.7s; }
  .orb-pulse:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 5.4s; }

  @keyframes breathe {
    0%, 100% { transform: scale(1);    opacity: 0.7; }
    50%       { transform: scale(1.12); opacity: 1; }
  }
  @keyframes pulse-out {
    0%   { transform: scale(0.8); opacity: 0.3; }
    100% { transform: scale(1.8); opacity: 0; }
  }

  .orb-label {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -2.5rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    font-family: 'Spectral', serif;
    font-weight: 200;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mist);
    opacity: 0.5;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(123,158,192,0.3);
    color: var(--paper);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: 'Spectral', serif;
    font-weight: 200;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 1.6s 1.3s ease forwards;
    transition: background 0.5s, border-color 0.5s, color 0.5s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-cta::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(123,158,192,0.06);
    transform: translateX(-100%);
    transition: transform 0.5s ease;
  }
  .hero-cta:hover::before { transform: translateX(0); }
  .hero-cta:hover { border-color: rgba(123,158,192,0.6); }

  .cta-icon {
    width: 20px; height: 20px;
    fill: var(--glow);
  }

  /* Scroll indicator */
  .scroll-hint {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 2.5rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeIn 2s 2.5s ease forwards;
  }
  .scroll-line {
    width: 1px;
    height: 50px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, var(--glow));
    animation: scroll-grow 2s 2.5s ease forwards, scroll-pulse 3s 4.5s ease-in-out infinite;
    transform-origin: top;
    transform: scaleY(0);
  }
  @keyframes scroll-grow { to { transform: scaleY(1); } }
  @keyframes scroll-pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.4; }
    50%       { opacity: 1; }
  }
  .scroll-hint span {
    font-size: 0.55rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mist);
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  /* ─── DIVIDER ───────────────────────────────── */
  .divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 80px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, rgba(168,180,196,0.3), transparent);
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  /* ─── ABOUT / DESCRIPTION ───────────────────── */
  .about {
    padding: clamp(4rem, 10vw, 8rem) clamp(2rem, 8vw, 6rem);
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .section-tag {
    font-family: 'Spectral', serif;
    font-weight: 200;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.4em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .about-lead {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.4rem);
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--paper);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .about-body {
    font-family: 'Spectral', serif;
    font-weight: 200;
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 2vw, 1.05rem);
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: rgba(240,237,232,0.6);
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* ─── QUALITIES ─────────────────────────────── */
  .qualities {
    padding: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem) clamp(2rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 1px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(168,180,196,0.1);
    position: relative;
  }
  .qualities::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: -1px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(123,158,192,0.08), transparent 40%, rgba(200,169,110,0.05));
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .quality {
    padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
    border-right: 1px solid rgba(168,180,196,0.08);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(168,180,196,0.08);
    transition: background 0.6s;
  }
  .quality:hover { background: rgba(123,158,192,0.04); }
  .quality:last-child { border-right: none; }

  .quality-num {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    color: var(--glow);
    opacity: 0.5;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .quality-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2.5vw, 1.6rem);
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }
  .quality-desc {
    font-family: 'Spectral', serif;
    font-weight: 200;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(240,237,232,0.45);
  }

  /* ─── JOURNEY / TIMELINE ────────────────────── */
  .journey {
    padding: clamp(4rem, 10vw, 8rem) clamp(2rem, 8vw, 6rem);
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .journey-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }
  .journey-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 3rem;
  }
  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.5rem;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom,
      var(--glow),
      rgba(123,158,192,0.2) 60%,
      transparent);
  }

  .timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    opacity: 0.6;
    transition: opacity 0.4s;
  }
  .timeline-item:hover { opacity: 1; }

  .timeline-dot {
    position: absolute;
    left: -3.22rem;
    top: 0.3rem;
    width: 8px; height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--glow);
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(123,158,192,0.6);
    transition: box-shadow 0.4s;
  }
  .timeline-item:hover .timeline-dot {
    box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(123,158,192,1);
  }
  .timeline-item:nth-child(2) .timeline-dot { background: var(--mist); }
  .timeline-item:nth-child(3) .timeline-dot { background: rgba(168,180,196,0.5); }
  .timeline-item:nth-child(4) .timeline-dot { background: rgba(168,180,196,0.25); }

  .timeline-time {
    font-family: 'Spectral', serif;
    font-weight: 200;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.35em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--glow);
    opacity: 0.7;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    display: block;
  }
  .timeline-label {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.5vw, 1.4rem);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .timeline-note {
    font-family: 'Spectral', serif;
    font-weight: 200;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(240,237,232,0.45);
  }

  /* ─── CREATOR ───────────────────────────────── */
  .creator {
    padding: clamp(4rem, 10vw, 8rem) clamp(2rem, 8vw, 6rem);
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .creator { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
  }

  .creator-aside {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .creator-sigil {
    width: 120px; height: 120px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(123,158,192,0.2);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 40% 35%, rgba(123,158,192,0.1), transparent 70%);
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--mist);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .creator-stat {
    text-align: center;
    font-family: 'Spectral', serif;
    font-weight: 200;
  }
  .creator-stat strong {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 2rem;
    display: block;
    color: var(--gold);
  }
  .creator-stat span {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mist);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .creator-content {}
  .creator-name {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .creator-role {
    font-family: 'Spectral', serif;
    font-weight: 200;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--mist);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }
  .creator-bio {
    font-family: 'Spectral', serif;
    font-weight: 200;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: rgba(240,237,232,0.55);
  }

  /* ─── LISTEN CTA ────────────────────────────── */
  .listen-section {
    padding: clamp(5rem, 12vw, 10rem) clamp(2rem, 8vw, 6rem);
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .listen-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 600px; height: 300px;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center bottom, rgba(30,60,120,0.3), transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .listen-kicker {
    font-family: 'Spectral', serif;
    font-weight: 200;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 3vw, 1.5rem);
    color: var(--mist);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: block;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }
  .listen-heading {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 7vw, 5rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .listen-heading em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--mist);
  }

  .listen-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.2rem;
    padding: 1.3rem 3.5rem;
    background: rgba(123,158,192,0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(123,158,192,0.35);
    color: var(--paper);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: 'Spectral', serif;
    font-weight: 200;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: border-color 0.5s, background 0.5s;
  }
  .listen-btn::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(123,158,192,0.1), transparent);
    transform: translateX(-100%);
    transition: transform 0.8s ease;
  }
  .listen-btn:hover::before { transform: translateX(100%); }
  .listen-btn:hover {
    border-color: rgba(123,158,192,0.7);
    background: rgba(123,158,192,0.15);
  }

  .spotify-icon {
    width: 20px; height: 20px;
    fill: #1DB954;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ─── FOOTER ────────────────────────────────── */
  footer {
    padding: 3rem clamp(2rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(168,180,196,0.08);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .footer-brand {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--mist);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }
  .footer-note {
    font-family: 'Spectral', serif;
    font-weight: 200;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mist);
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  /* ─── UTILITIES ─────────────────────────────── */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; }
    to   { opacity: 1; }
  }

  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    transition: opacity 0.9s ease, transform 0.9s ease;
  }
  .reveal.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: none;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Custom cursor -->
<div class="cursor" id="cursor"></div>
<div class="cursor-ring" id="cursorRing"></div>

<!-- Background layers -->
<div class="aurora"></div>
<div class="stars" id="stars"></div>

<!-- ─── HERO ──────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="hero">
  <span class="hero-eyebrow">An immersive overnight experience</span>

  <h1 class="hero-title">
    DeepPulse<em>Sleep Experience</em>
  </h1>

  <p class="hero-subtitle">8 hours of live music<br>designed for sleep</p>

  <div class="orb-wrap">
    <div class="orb-pulse"></div>
    <div class="orb-pulse"></div>
    <div class="orb"></div>
    <div class="orb-inner"></div>
    <span class="orb-label">Breathe</span>
  </div>

  <a href="https://lemoscomposer.com/sleepexperience" class="hero-cta" style="opacity:0.7; cursor:default; pointer-events:none;">
    <svg class="cta-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <rect x="3" y="9" width="18" height="13" rx="1"/><path d="M8 9V6a4 4 0 018 0v3"/>
    </svg>
    Tickets — Coming Soon
  </a>

  <div class="scroll-hint">
    <div class="scroll-line"></div>
    <span>Descend</span>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- ─── ABOUT ─────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="about">
  <span class="section-tag reveal">What this is</span>
  <p class="about-lead reveal">
    This is not a traditional concert.<br>
    It is an invitation to disconnect,<br>lie down, and allow sound to become<br>part of the body's natural rhythm.
  </p>
  <p class="about-body reveal">
    Blending ambient composition, subtle piano, and natural soundscapes, 
    the sound unfolds as a continuous environment that slows perception, 
    quiets mental activity, and supports the transition into sleep. 
    Across the night, the experience evolves from soft, organic textures 
    into minimal, sustained sound designed to maintain a stable 
    and uninterrupted state of rest.
  </p>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- ─── QUALITIES ─────────────────────────────── -->
<section style="padding: 0 clamp(1rem,4vw,2rem); position:relative; z-index:10;">
  <div class="qualities">
    <div class="quality reveal">
      <span class="quality-num">01</span>
      <h3 class="quality-title">Ambient Composition</h3>
